metadata.name: Hustler
metadata.description: The hustler Strycorn knows the exact difference between "doing shit" and "getting shit done", he is stretsmart and he won't settle for anything that doesn't meet his expectations. There is only one direction for him and that is upwards, once he sets his mind on something he will work hard to make it happen. And that means dealing with all the punches life throws at you and growing with each experience.
